{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-chenfeng-007__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-chenfeng-007", "source_id": "guofeng-chenfeng-007__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "poem", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·陳風·007.1", "text_original": "防有鵲巢，邛有旨苕。誰侜予美，心焉忉忉。\n中唐有甓，邛有旨鷊。誰侜予美，心焉惕惕。", "text_normalized": "防有鵲巢，邛有旨苕。誰侜予美，心焉忉忉。\n中唐有甓，邛有旨鷊。誰侜予美，心焉惕惕。", "notes": "防有鵲巢 Chinese poem 1."}
